# PolicyCodex onboarding scratch space - never commit. The app stages an
# uploaded retention PDF and an extraction draft here during the wizard. The app
# only ever `git add`s explicit paths, so this is defense-in-depth for any
# manual git use in the diocese repo.
.policycodex-staging/

# PolicyCodex ingest manifest (AI-17) - per-host state, never commit. Records
# the prior inventory pass's source-file hashes so the next run can diff
# against them and re-process only added/changed sources. The companion
# .policycodex/config.yaml file (committed by onboarding) lives in the same
# directory but is tracked; only this single file is ignored.
.policycodex/ingest-manifest.json
